{"tid":1024693,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"同女友性生活唔夾","createTime":"2019-02-16T18:11:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-18T00:12:00.000Z","uid":43252,"like":1,"dislike":23,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"df2dcc406c4c9113ce45a00cfbf0df46f70af26e","tid":1024693,"uid":43252,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-16T18:11:59.000Z","msg":"有疑問 借朋友ac po上黎 <br />\n<br />\n我係男，我同我女朋友拍左拖2年半，真係想同佢一生一世，因為佢真係好女仔，但我地性方面唔係好夾<br />\n同佢一齊一年嗰時都好地地，佢都算主動，有主動拖我攬我，但依家就好日都唔攬我一次，之前都有親熱嘅，因為大家都承諾左結婚前唔破處，但大家都要捽下豆打下飛機含下咁，但依家佢真係零興趣，今天都只係搞過3次，手指都數得出，仲要係佢冇乜反應嗰種。<br />\n我有諗過可能係熱情期過左，所以我都有試過製造啲新鮮感同浪漫，但都唔得，佢都冇興趣，我地都有傾過依個問題，佢話唔知點主動，叫佢學下就發脾氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我有認真諗過，有七成離婚都因性生活不協調，而我唔想成為其中一個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />好困惑，唔知點做好"},{"pid":"3f1e466e938994f62e9332e2551fbfff0ff7be71","tid":1024693,"uid":43252,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-16T18:17:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc901063145561a8ab12a3bf0be855158a38b462","tid":1024693,"uid":54595,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-16T18:18:36.000Z","msg":"lm 有同樣煩惱<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6afb621da318f50c41947ef7358cdb4f88bc705a","tid":1024693,"uid":125751,"like":21,"dislike":1,"score":20,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-16T18:20:21.000Z","msg":"今天都係搞過三次係咪意思<br />\n即係一日三次？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"26b715953f9774e2b09eed9550548b246d364d41","tid":1024693,"uid":198035,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-16T18:21:43.000Z","msg":"買粒震蛋過佢"},{"pid":"122a39dc2b05986649158afeaca8afc2df61c264","tid":1024693,"uid":208581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-16T18:26:54.000Z","msg":"幾歲先，廿到炆就快快手搵過件喇"},{"pid":"91182903e0fc4526f12e915a668db58